title: Renovated Lakeview East 1Bed, AMZING VIEW, Rooftop, Parking Available
posting_body: ['Beautiful condo-quality 1 bedroom on the 15th floor of a mid-rise building.', 'Located in the the middle of prime Lakeview East!', 'Close to the Broadway, Clark, & Diversey corridor.', 'Shopping, restaurants, and coffee right at your doorstep.', 'Plus, easy lakefront access!', 'Short walk to the Wellington Brown Line station.', '- Renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, extra counter and cabinet space, and granite countertops.', '- Amazing natural light with beautiful city view.', '- Bathroom with extra vanity storage.', '- Wall AC units in both the living and bedrooms.', '- Card-operated laundry in building.', '- Rooftop Patio with 360 city views!', '(Must see for the Air & Water Show, 4th of July Fireworks, etc)', '- Secure entry, elevator building.', '- Package room.', '- Garage parking (additional monthly cost, ask me about availability)', '- Bike storage.', '- Pet friendly!!', '- Gas and heat included.', '**445 W Wellington**', 'Just added to the market and will not last!']
